# Login Debug & Fix Checklist

- [ ] Run diagnostic probe on Frontend and Backend VMs (`probe-vms.ps1`)
- [ ] Verify Backend process (Server) is running on `10.172.19.15`
- [ ] Check if Backend is listening on port 5000
- [ ] Inspect Nginx error logs on `10.172.19.16`
- [ ] Restart/Start Backend service if necessary
- [ ] Verify connectivity via `Invoke-WebRequest`
- [ ] Final browser login test
